Fear and Loathing in Las Vegas;;89;;50;;R;;Raoul Duke (Johnny Depp) and his attorney Dr. Gonzo (Benicio Del Toro) drive a red convertible across the Mojave desert to Las Vegas with a suitcase full of drugs to cover a motorcycle race. As their consumption of drugs increases at an alarming rate, the stoned duo trash their hotel room and fear legal repercussions. Duke begins to drive back to L.A., but after an odd run-in with a cop (Gary Busey), he returns to Sin City and continues his wild drug binge.;;Comedy;;Terry Gilliam;;1998;;Johnny Depp,Benicio Del Toro,Craig Bierko,Ellen Barkin,Gary Busey,Cameron Diaz,Flea,Mark Harmon,Katherine Helmond,Michael Jeter,Penn Jillette,Lyle Lovett,Tobey Maguire,Christina Ricci,Harry Dean Stanton,Tim Thomerson;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fear_and_loathing_in_las_vegas